  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00001",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王允上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00002",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "调和鼎鼐，位列三台。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00003",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "老夫，王允。唐室驾前为臣，官拜当朝首相，夫人陈氏，膝下无儿，所生三女：长女金钏，匹配苏龙；次女银钏，匹配魏虎；只有三女宝钏，尚未婚配。本月二日，曾在十字街前，高搭彩楼，抛球招赘。吾只道打着哪家王孙公子，不料打着了花郎薛平贵。想吾儿乃是千金之体，怎能与那花郎匹配，不免将女儿唤出。",
      "text_length": 139
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00004",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "院子暗上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00005",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "将这门亲事打退，另配王孙公子，免得耽误吾儿终身。家院，后堂传话：请三姑娘出堂。",
      "text_length": 39
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00006",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "院子"
      ],
      "text": "后堂传话：请三姑娘出堂。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00007",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "丫鬟"
      ],
      "text": "请三姑娘。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00008",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "来了。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00009",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王宝钏、丫鬟同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00010",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "十字街前搭彩楼，为招夫婿抛彩球。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00011",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "爹爹万福。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00012",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "吾儿少礼，一旁坐下。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00013",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "谢坐。爹爹唤女儿出来，有何训教？",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00014",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "吾儿在十字街前，抛球招赘，可知打的哪家王孙公子？",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00015",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "孩儿不知。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00016",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "就是那花郎平贵。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00017",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "也是儿命该如此。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00018",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "依为父之见，莫若将此门亲事打退，另配王孙公子。不知吾儿，意下如何？",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00019",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "爹爹说哪里话来，想孩儿既然抛球招赘，就是凭天所定。今日慢说是打着花郎平贵，就是打着一块顽石，孩儿也要抱……",
      "text_length": 53
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00020",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "抱什么？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00021",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "抱他三年五载，以表恩爱之情。丫鬟，打坐向前！",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00022",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "为父与你讲话，敢是同为父赌气？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00023",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "孩儿焉敢与爹爹赌气。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00024",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "既然不是与为父赌气，就该退去此门亲事。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00025",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "慢说是爹爹之命，就是皇王旨意，也难更改。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00026",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "儿就该掌嘴！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00027",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "小奴才说此话全然不想，不由得年迈人怒满胸膛。你大姐配苏龙户部执掌，你二姐配魏虎兵部侍郎。惟有你小冤家性情倔强，千金女配花郎怎度时光？",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00028",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "老爹爹说此话全不思想，细听着孩儿说端详：秦甘罗一十二身为宰相，姜子牙八十二才遇文王。你莫道薛平贵他花郎模样，贫穷人发迹比富还强。",
      "text_length": 64
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00029",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "薛平贵生来命运低，每日里在长街去讨食。半截褴衫罩不住身体，遮住东来露着西。",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00030",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "昔日里有一个孟姜女，他与那范郎送寒衣。哭倒了长城十数里，至今留名万古题。",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00031",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "前朝事儿——",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00032",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "休提起，千金怎为花郎妻？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00033",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "昔日韩信曾受困，登台拜帅落美名。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00034",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "既知前朝韩元帅，未央宫死的是什么人？",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00035",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "未央宫死的是韩信，可知那张良与苏秦？",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00036",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "沈宏也会把亲退，另配姻缘为何情？",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00037",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "沈宏虽然把亲退，他乃是不义不肖人。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00038",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "要退要退偏要退，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00039",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "你不能不能万不能。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00040",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "两件宝衣来脱下，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00041",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮流水板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "再与爹爹把话明。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00042",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "请问爹爹，这两件宝衣，是哪里来的？",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00043",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "乃是圣上所赐。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00044",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "圣上所赐，但不知为着何来？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00045",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "不过是念在君臣之意。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00046",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "好吓！圣上倒有君臣之意，难道爹爹，就无有父女之情了么？",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00047",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "吾儿将这门亲事打退，慢说这两件宝衣，就是府内的金银，也任儿搬取。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00048",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "孩儿不要了。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00049",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "老爹爹不念父女意，孩儿焉有儿女情？忙把宝衣齐脱下，",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00050",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王宝钏脱宫装，捧衣看，掷与王允。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00051",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "递于嫌贫爱富人。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00052",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "儿吓，为父嫌贫爱富，爱的是哪一个？",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00053",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "孩儿不知。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00054",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "为的就是你这个奴才呀！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00055",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "爹爹不必把儿为，孩儿不做那无义人。三从四德是本分，怎敢爱富来嫌贫。要与爹爹三击掌，从今后不登相府门。",
      "text_length": 50
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00056",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "宝钏说话太无情，到叫老夫怒生嗔。今日与吾三击掌，从今后就断了父女情。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00057",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "非是孩儿心太狠，只为不贤留骂名。悲切切我这里三击掌，",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00058",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "活活气坏了年迈人。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00059",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "叫丫鬟带路后堂进，",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00060",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "你往哪里去？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00061",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "到后堂拜别老娘亲。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00062",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "丫鬟好好把守庭堂，若有人去往后堂，定要打断尔的狗腿！",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00063",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "孩儿不去了。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00064",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "老爹爹不许吾把老娘见，倒叫宝钏痛在心。含悲忍泪出府门，",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00065",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "丫鬟"
      ],
      "text": "三姑娘要往哪里去？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00066",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "去到寒窑中把身存。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00067",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "丫鬟"
      ],
      "text": "我们实实舍不得三姑娘。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00068",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "你们舍不得三姑娘，你三姑娘是怎么舍得了你们？",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00069",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "王宝钏"
      ],
      "text": "这丫鬟们她倒有主仆义，恋恋不舍两泪淋。咬定牙关出相府，",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01023004_e00070",
      "play_id": "01023004",
      "scene_id": "01023004_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "丫鬟"
      ],
      "text": "送三姑娘。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
